%N A393742 Number of free polyominoes in the {8,6} tessellation of the hyperbolic plane.
%F A393742 a(n) = P{p,q}(n) (the number of {p,q} polyominoes of size n) is equal to P{p,oo}(n) for n <= q; also P{p,q}(q+1) = P{p,oo}(q+1) + floor((p-1)/2) - floor((3+q(p-2))/2), where . In this case, p=8, q=6 and P{p,oo} = A389937.
%Y A393742 Cf. A393739, A393740, A393741, A393743, A393744, A389937.
